README.md
🧪 core_pattern.json (Concept)
The JSON file defines the structural logic of the system:
Step cycles (8 / 10 / 11)
Layer definitions
Trigger rules per log layer
Pattern mapping instructions
This file acts as the source of truth for rhythm generation.
🎹 MIDI Generator
The generator script converts the JSON structure into MIDI:
Reads cycle definitions
Assigns notes per layer
Outputs standard MIDI file format
Designed for DAWs (BandLab, FL Studio, Ableton, etc.)
🎧 How to Use
Clone the repository
Open percussion_orbit.mid in any DAW
Assign instruments:
Sub Log → Kick / 808 / sub bass
Rhythm Log → Log drum / bass percussion
Accent Log → Hats / percussion FX
Listen to phase interaction between cycles
🔥 Key Idea
Orbit House is not a loop-based system.
It is a:
phase-based generative rhythm engine
Groove is created through interaction, not repetition.
